{
  "stem": "19807.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they had it in Sofia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were no mikvahs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So until the age of five or six, I would go with my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after I was certain age, of course, I would go with my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- that was the ritual.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have showers inside the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're lucky to have indoor, you know, facilities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So weekly or as often as we could, I would go with my father to the Turkish bath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, on Fridays, would go to the Turkish bath.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a ritual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had several of them in-- in Plovdiv.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of them was right in the middle of the Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was called, I remember, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- but it was a ritual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the Bulgarians-- those baths were still from-- from Turkish time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if you recall, Bulgaria was a crossroads as well as Turkey, for the Byzantine Empire, for the Romans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And baths, it was a ritual with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very modern, with mosaics and with tiles, and with this-- now, another ritual-- they would have big, husky men in the men's area and heavy-set ladies for the ladies areas, that They would wear something on their hands and there would be straps through their waist and from waist up, they'll be-- they'll be naked.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the men, we would go and those men were big, very strong.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after we were into the steam, they would come and they rub your skin to make sure that nothing unclean was left on the skin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when you left there, you were clean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to call them-- and the-- the word in there was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
